**Workflow:**
User -> Planner;
Planner -> WebSearcher;
WebSearcher -> Summarizer;
Summarizer -> End.

**Description:**
First, the Planner analyzes the query and creates a search strategy to identify the dinosaur-related Featured Article promoted in November 2016 and its nominator. The WebSearcher executes this strategy through iterative web searches, first locating the article and then extracting nomination details. Finally, the Summarizer compiles the findings into a concise answer.
